<title>USA: TCI to broadcast Playboy service.</title>
<headline>TCI to broadcast Playboy service.</headline>
<dateline>BEVERLY HILLS, Calif. 1997-03-19</dateline>
<text>
<p>Playboy Entertainment Group on Tuesday said it signed a deal with cable T.V. provider Tele-Communications Inc that will launch Playboy's pay-per-view service, AdulTVision, on TCI systems.</p>
<p>Financial details were undisclosed.</p>
<p>AdulTVision broadcasts adult-themed movies to consumers in 90-minute pay-per-view blocks. The service is currently available in more than 2.7 million cable households and 2.2 million homes with television reception via satellite.</p>
<p>Playboy Entertainment Group is a wholly-owned subsidiary of Playboy Enterprises Inc.</p>
</text>
